Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.29,0:04:31.38,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,0)}口ずさめたら
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.71,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,聞いて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.96,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,世界がほどける音が
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.38,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,かけてくる
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.72,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,かけてくる
